{"tid":165992,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"生命倒數...","createTime":"2017-03-21T18:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T05:13:31.000Z","uid":93434,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f96a58ca4af1e67648c1c750b9715883f5577e39","tid":165992,"uid":93434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:21:37.000Z","msg":"真人真事,求各位巴絲俾d建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一半突發患病,醫生話最壞打算係剩番幾個月...<br />\n咩病就唔講,唔想撞到識的人<br />\n由我知道佢有事開始,我日日都好唔開心,一提起個病我就忍唔住喊..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫生叫佢呢段時間開開心心,想做就做<br />\n我好希望可以同佢開開心心走到最後,<br />\n佢都話好想開心好想去玩,<br />\n目前情況係佢精神唔錯行得走得,<br />\n各位巴絲可唔可以俾d建議我有咩地方可以同佢去玩? 動又好靜又好,唔太劇烈就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係我唔想諗,我而家剩係識唔開心同喊,身邊又無人可以講,我自己工作上的野又未搞掂,我可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好希望好希望奇蹟會出現...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出緊post我又忍唔住喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a7e8da558932e37fd3ca45307afc59e641fd9d","tid":165992,"uid":9964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:24:25.000Z","msg":"去旅行<br />\n做尐死前想做既野 跳飛機玩降落傘又好 <br />\n去拉下老虎條尾又好<br />\n去睇下VR AV又好 之後你同佢做愛又好<br />\n陪佢鳩玩下<br />\n唔知你幾歲<br />\n但因為唔想令自己後悔 所以玩盡 <br />\n就幾多歲都要識"},{"pid":"ceebc39f46506657cefbb85b32562e3517c8ca3c","tid":165992,"uid":6182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:25:11.000Z","msg":"或者去下短線旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日本台灣睇下景影下相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbetween 加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8776e2aabdeb21c584461d6aba7c17d153200e5","tid":165992,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:25:19.000Z","msg":"請個假陪佢去旅行<br />\n香港真係太細 要去既都應該去哂"},{"pid":"a8216bf3dd9b2c3717752897c458167e9c8462a8","tid":165992,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:26:30.000Z","msg":"你有方法可以幫佢延續生命"},{"pid":"b9812834b2223aa2ce18d8313c6f69c7fa353b09","tid":165992,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:26:37.000Z","msg":"行下公園 曬下太陽<br />\n有咩心願 了埋佢<br />\n<br />\n祝福佢 希望真係有奇跡出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448f934af0047b6ced8d7b19031f6bc537c09c75","tid":165992,"uid":41107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:27:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4484f22f21534fdef159623ca9663bf2d247d56","tid":165992,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:27:49.000Z","msg":"其實有你同屋企人陪住佢<br />\n佢都會好開心<br />\n同平時一樣<br />\n陪下佢同屋企人飲茶 傾計<br />\n一齊煲劇<br />\n陪佢搵下朋友吹水<br />\nsupport"},{"pid":"2ed570317fda1f2477e972dfc04826c845bafe1b","tid":165992,"uid":87064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:30:34.000Z","msg":"會唔會可以出走下去下外地?<br />\n想問兩位幾歲左右?"},{"pid":"8ab28fa783f28da2204a3f89b42be8a2b0f6bd69","tid":165992,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:30:43.000Z","msg":"能力可以嘅話 佢喜歡去邊就倍佢去<br />\n希望佢吉人天相  有奇蹟出現"},{"pid":"db7cde4315357f4d89172b49f766d88b949d5aa4","tid":165992,"uid":93434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下咩病 血呀 骨髓 肝之類 睇下有無人幫到手</blockquote><br />\n冇方法,太突然壞到唔做得手術...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講太多個病啦,雖然佢平時唔上連登,但我唔知佢會唔會撞左入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3e695d266338b84477d1b74cc0dd73a9d7a49e","tid":165992,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:33:44.000Z","msg":"我教大家 當人哋同你講好唔開心 你要應佢我好明白你而家嘅感受 我會陪住你<br />\n<br />\n唔撚去同佢講唔好唔開心 你試吓點樣點樣<br />\n<br />\n其實人都係想有人陪"},{"pid":"98a724540e08050d8a3b7cef89466d7c4fedac2b","tid":165992,"uid":93436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:34:59.000Z","msg":"唔好擔心咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申cancer患者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea89ba93687f6d043b14683b3c7d6f50c660c82e","tid":165992,"uid":93434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請個假陪佢去旅行<br />\n香港真係太細 要去既都應該去哂</blockquote><br />\n我成日請假陪佢,<br />\n我都知去旅行好開心,係一個好好的回憶,但我唔去得.... 原因就...不要問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港係細,或者有d好地方我漏左,講黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6252c5c44f3018623513e509fb5d493d8c7eb1c","tid":165992,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:39:08.000Z","msg":"你信唔信都好 我平時有個能力就係心想事成（通常都得）住邊區 我祝福下佢應該可能會冇事 認真的 可能你覺得膠"},{"pid":"6949c88f1e0bb0ed63506c2ceef3c89ef5f04d06","tid":165992,"uid":93434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會可以出走下去下外地?<br />\n想問兩位幾歲左右?</blockquote><br />\n廿幾<br />\n我唔去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed530ddf1fe00bafff3097ea995508b223c1132","tid":165992,"uid":93434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好擔心咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申cancer患者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打而家點呀?"},{"pid":"1cbec68838ce6151099fc46f0f5e43d181dfb093","tid":165992,"uid":93434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:42:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你信唔信都好 我平時有個能力就係心想事成（通常都得）住邊區 我祝福下佢應該可能會冇事 認真的 可能你覺得膠</blockquote><br />\n巴打,麻煩你祝福下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"